            name: "Hyperion",
            baseImgUrl: "/hyperion_bg.jpg",
            baseText: "Hyperion",
            subText: "Saturn's irregular-shaped moon with a unique, sponge-like appearance, covered in deep craters and lacking any substantial atmosphere, making it a mysterious and captivating object of scientific study.",
